data.description: Great Opportunity for Investors or Buyers who can put in some sweat equity.  Cozy. Sweet. Good starter home. Lots of Natural Light and Wood floors! Large, screened in porch adds to the livability! Spacious kitchen - plenty of cabinets.  Manageable yard space. Convenient to Hwy 360 and Keysville Va, yet in a country setting. Will not qualify for gov't loans, and this is reflected in the excellent price.
